testcase.name: when dismissing delete dialog in loaded state should clear the id to delete
when initializing should emit Loaded state with the expected models
when delete item button clicked and in loaded state should update the state
when deleting item in loaded state with no id to delete should do nothing
when initializing empty should emit Loaded state with the expected models
when add button clicked should navigate to the edit screen
when dismissing delete dialog not in loaded state should do nothing
when deleting item not in loaded state should do nothing
when delete item button clicked and not in loaded state should do nothing
when already initialized should not fetch configuration
when item clicked should navigate to the explorer screen
when edit item button clicked should navigate to the edit screen
when deleting item in loaded state with id to delete should invoke delete use case
